---
title: Apricot-Glazed Mumbai Beef Rump with Veggie Couscous & Cucumber Raita
description: This beef rump is sweet, spiced and very nice. When using an apricot sauce to glaze beef it’s best to pair it with a fluffy couscous
to help absorb all those flavours. Include a cucumber raita to cool off after your tastebuds are blown away.

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving.*
